's end, only the sections with at least three spaces filled will be worth points!</p>\n\n<p>Do you like nice plants, or do you prefer cute cats? Will you focus your attention on completing columns, or will you try to run for the shelves?</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<p>COMPONENTS:<br />\nCardboard:<br />\n4 Player boards (14x14cm, dry erase)</p>\n\n<p>Plastic:<br />\n6 Dice: 16mm white acrylic six-sided custom dice (turquoise Trophy, green Plant leaf, dark blue Book, yellow Meeple, red Cat, Joker (all 5 colors)</p>\n\n<p>4 Dry Erase Markers (black)</p>\n\n<p>Rule book (8 p.).</p>\n\n","website":{"url":"https://craniocreations.it/en/product/My-Shelfie-The-Dice-Game","title":"My Shelfie The Dice Game on Cranio Creations Website"},"imageid":"7971302","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__small/img/2J62bh9RC_JXWfNKVR6KQlTyHuU=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7971302.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__micro/img/BuSDZXtjp6oRLF9-DPmfOuSCS-w=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7971302.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__square/img/8__wI_UqLwjRZCTH0sdT4G0B68U=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7971302.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__tallthumb/img/cTHVWGT8zOJ0JrZ3e3fFpj0_888=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7971302.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__previewthumb/img/zH7Z44WR9AmeafaUuw59baHia74=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7971302.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__square200/img/GgwxVtVv5XaNNLQ6-fx2AyPTsWc=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic7971302.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-Vpjczb3jA__original/img/TQwFX7-pZlpABEG1t7lngQD6Nqk=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic7971302.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/7971302/my-shelfie-the-dice-game","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/2dArgx26TAFP-V